PUSMemoryLoad::MemBlockType Struct Reference

#include <PUSMemoryLoad.h>

List of all members.

Detailed Description

This structure describes one memory load block.

This structure is declared protected to allow the concrete implementations of the PUS memory load service to have direct access to it.
